From: sfalcon at fhcrc.org (Seth Falcon)
Date: Tue, 31 Oct 2006 12:42:45 -0800
Subject: [Bioc-devel] Nasty function collision
In-Reply-To: <45479F15.20809@med.umich.edu> (James W. MacDonald's message of
